name: select_option
description: Select one of the available options from the list.
parameters: {'option': "Which option do you want to select? ['Details', 'Starred', 'Archive', 'Delete', 'Help & feedback']"}

name: resend_message
description: Resend the most recently sent message to the selected contact.
parameters: {'contact_name': "Name of the contact to whom the message should be resent (e.g., 'Amy')", 'message_text': 'Text of the message to be resent'}

name: resend_selected_message
description: Resend the currently selected message to the intended contact.
parameters: {'contact_name': "Name of the contact to whom the message should be resent (e.g., 'Amy')", 'message_text': "Text of the message to be resent (e.g., 'HELLO.')"}
